        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:89:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/144/175",
        "text": [
          "١٤٤. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): يَنْزِلُ الصَّبْرُ عَلَى قَدْرِ الْمُصِيبَةِ، وَمَنْ ضَرَبَ يَدَهُ عَلَى فَخِذِهِ عِنْدَ مُصِيبَتِهِ حَبِطَ أجْرُهُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "144. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Endurance comes according to the affliction. He who beats his hand on the thigh in his affliction ruins all his good actions."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
